35 amount that will be distributed to the taxing unit under this chapter
36 during the ensuing calendar year, the department of local government
37 finance shall also determine the amount of general purpose revenue
38 allocated for economic development purposes that will be distributed
39 to each civil taxing unit, reduced by an amount that is equal to the
40 following percentages of the tax revenue that would otherwise be
41 allocated for economic development purposes and distributed to the
42 civil taxing unit:
