13 SECTION 38. IC 6-3.6-9-17.5, AS ADDED BY P.L.68-2025,
14 SECTION 171, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS
15 [EFFECTIVE JULY 1, 2027]: Sec. 17.5. After December 31, 2027, the
16 county's an adopting body's certified distribution amount for 2028
